---
---
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>🔒 ADMIN LOGIN</title>
    <style>
      body { background: #0c0c0c; color: #00ff41; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
      .login-box { border: 2px solid #00ff41; padding: 40px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ff41; position: relative; }
      
      /* 홈 버튼 스타일 */
      .home-btn { 
        display: inline-block; 
        margin-top: 20px; 
        color: #888; 
        text-decoration: none; 
        font-size: 0.8rem; 
        border: 1px solid #333; 
        padding: 5px 10px; 
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .home-btn:hover { color: #00ff41; border-color: #00ff41; background: rgba(0,255,65,0.1); }

      input { background: #000; border: 1px solid #00ff41; color: #00ff41; padding: 10px; width: 200px; outline: none; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 10px; }
      button { background: #00ff41; color: #000; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; margin-top: 20px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; }
      button:hover { background: #fff; }
      
      #admin-content { display: none; } 
      .hidden { display: none !important; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div id="login-form" class="login-box">
      <h2>[ ACCESS DENIED ]</h2>
      <p>관리자 인증 코드를 입력하세요.</p>
      <input type="password" id="password-input" placeholder="PASSCODE" onkeypress="if(event.keyCode==13) checkPassword()"/>
      <br />
      <button onclick="checkPassword()">ENTER</button>
      <br />
      <a href="/otomadbloghub/" class="home-btn">[ RETURN TO HOME ]</a>
    </div>

    <div id="admin-content" class="login-box" style="text-align: left; width: 600px;">
      <h1 style="color: #ff3e00;">🛠️ OPERATOR CONSOLE</h1>
      <p>> 관리자 권한이 승인되었습니다.</p>
      <hr style="border: 1px solid #333;" />
      
      <h3>1. 제보 내역 확인</h3>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/너의_시트_ID" target="_blank" style="color: #fff; background: #444; padding: 8px 15px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px;">스프레드시트 열기</a>

      <h3>2. 데이터 업데이트</h3>
      <p><code>src/data.json</code> 파일에 데이터를 추가하고 Push 하세요.</p>
      
      <hr style="border: 1px solid #333; margin-top: 30px;" />
      <a href="/otomadbloghub/" class="home-btn" style="color: #00ff41; border-color: #00ff41;">[ EXIT TO HOME ]</a>
    </div>

    <script is:inline>
      const ADMIN_PASSCODE = "bozi4973"; // 💡 여기서 비밀번호를 바꾸세요!

      function checkPassword() {
        const input = document.getElementById('password-input').value;
        const loginForm = document.getElementById('login-form');
        const adminContent = document.getElementById('admin-content');

        if (input === ADMIN_PASSCODE) {
          loginForm.classList.add('hidden');
          adminContent.style.display = 'block';
        } else {
          alert("경고: 잘못된 패스코드입니다.");
        }
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>